<plot>In Yunmeng, a rural city in the Hubei Province,there's a theater: a teahouse where old men gather amongst the shadows of the past, drinking tea and playing cards. There, an ancient art takes place and brings magic back into everyday life. But China's growth towards a new century brings up a few questions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?407544</url></doc>
